  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (NC-6 clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Two factors (Numerical solver error; Use error) are marked not-applicable with documented rationale. All remaining eleven factors are fully assessed with requiredLevel and achievedLevel integers; all achievedLevels meet or exceed requiredLevels. Decision: Accepted.",
