      "description": "Assessment is scoped to the FDA benchmark centrifugal pump geometry operating in VAD flow regimes (flow rates 2–8 L/min, rotational speeds 2000–3500 RPM). Extrapolation to other pump geometries or paediatric flow conditions is outside scope."
