      "rationale": "Input parameters used in validation simulations are shown to be equivalent to those in the COU simulations within stated tolerances. Fluid viscosity, density, and hemolysis model coefficients are identical; pump geometry is the same CAD model. Haematocrit differences between validation (35%) and COU (40%) are within the UQ propagation range.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
